item.title: CVE-2018-13390|2024-08-05T09:00:35.117Z -- atlassian -- cloudtoken
item.description: Unauthenticated access to cloudtoken daemon on Linux via network from version 0.1.1 before version 0.1.24 allows attackers on the same subnet to gain temporary AWS credentials for the users' roles.
